metadata.name: who am i?
metadata.description:
the average life expectancy here in japan is 85. i collected 85 images of my dear friend that i photographed throughout the years and trained this dataset through a stylegan to create ai generated versions of him.

"who am i?" explores the idea of change and the versions of ourselves that is created through suffering. you face the harsh realities of life forthrightly and do your best to acclimate, or maybe you dont. regardless, what do you lose in the process?

who am i? what have i become?
